<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/c00a55337afa4c408b8ad653a21a1014.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>动作3、箭步蹲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201107/b2b0b6e16a354df5be2e6856c997ba5f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>动作4、跪姿侧抬腿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201107/6866f26c7b6d41aeb110bdf3faa20914.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
